#FBF to a video you guys loved so much 🛼😜 it was a beautiful January 1st sunset in Miami, the first sunset of 2021! 💗🌅 when I posted this video we were at 80k (?) now we are nearly 120k and i just wanna say thank you so much for all the love and support 🙏🏽😍
-
Shoutout to @paz_sw for following me around on his skateboard, risking it all😂🤍
-
🔗 in bí0

node.text:
Organic🌱 no photoshop, no surgical/injectables, no waist trainers, no teas, no protein powders, no bcaas, pre workouts etc. 😊 i’m very happy with the natural fitness route i took! I tell you guys all the time that fitness is a billion dollar industry👀 all you really need is consistent  proper exercise and a healthy balanced diet🌱 i don’t fall off training, because the way i do it is sustainable, my joints feel heathy and i’m always making progress 😉 
-
🔗 in bio for workouts & nutrition🍑

node.text:
The many phases of a b🍑🍑ty !
i don’t want to be perfect, i just want to be real and relatable 😌
As you scroll through IG and see gorgeous perfect pictures, don’t forget we all here posing in the best angles and lighting. And sadly some facetune/photoshop for extra unattainable perfection😕 which is fine, do what makes u happy.... but photoshopping and then selling products / workout programs, waist trainers, supplements, skin products etc. is just plain sad to me... please just consider how your altered images may affect the way women view themselves and reality. I understand that you’re not responsible for how your brand makes others feel, but it takes nothing out of you to be honest.
-
🔗 in 🅱️❗️🅾️ 😌
